      <div class="msgContentFrame">I'm only rank 14 THM and CON, and from what I can tell so far, both caster classes are quite strong in the solo department.  As mentioned previously, it is certainly worthwhile to spend a bit of time doing some crafting, as the physical experience gained is very high (like 1k per synth).  <br /> <br />With higher base stats, particularly in VIT and MND, you can hold your own against some pretty tough mobs.  I was doing Dodos in the Drybone area at rank 9, and have been doing Aldgoats near Bloodshore at rank 14 (phys. level 26).  <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV: Seij Koroshiya - Trabia <br />FFXI: Seijurohiko - Cerberus <i>(retired)</i> <br /> <br /><a href="HTTP://www.youtube.com/user/securitron1234" rel="external nofollow" title="www.youtube.com/user/securitron1234">YouTube Page</a></div></div>
